overview: Ahead of their concert at Yoyogi National Gymnasium First Gymnasium, the members enjoy talking while eating Kudo Yume's and Matsunaga Riai's favorite food. There is a lot of excitement playing roulette games! Then lastly, they get under their futons like on a school trip...?! The 25th DVD magazine is filled with the charm of the new Juice=Juice!  merchandise for the Juice=Juice CONCERT 2019 ~octopic!~.
title: Juice=Juice DVD Magazine Vol.25
